description: Tables showing a) the number of finished in year admission and discharge episodes where there was a primary or secondary diagnosis of malnutrition, b) the number of finished in year admission and discharge episodes where there was a primary or secondary diagnosis of nutritional anaemia, c) the number of finished in year admission and discharge episodes where there was a primary or secondary diagnosis of 'other nutritional deficiencies for National Health Service hospitals in England for the years 1997/98 to 2006/07 and d) the number of finished in year admission and discharge episodes for all hospital providers where there was a primary or secondary diagnosis of malnutrition, nutritional anaemia and nutritional deficiencies for 2006/07. 11 p.
